nd wireline businesses are primarily operated through telus communications company tcc the company offers business services including healthcare across wireless and wireline are supported through telus sales representatives product specialists independent dealers and online selfserve applications for small and mediumsized businesses smbs its business process outsourcing services are supported through sales representatives and client relationship management teams industry sector and symbol sector utilities industry integrated telecommunications services  nec subindustry na symbol nysetu cusip na web wwwteluscom capitalizationmarket cap  billionoutstanding shares average prices day moving avg  day moving avg  week range    petrailing pe ratio foreward pe ratio pe growth sales  book valueannual revenue  billionprice  sales book value  per shareprice  book dividendannual dividend dividend yield  profitabilityebidta  billionnet margins return on equity return on assets debtdebttoequity ratio current ratio quick ratio miscaverage volume  shsbeta short ratio    frequently asked questions for telus corporation nysetu what is telus corporations stock symbol telus corporation trades on the new york stock exchange nyse under the ticker symbol tu how often does telus corporation pay dividends what is the dividend yield for telus corporation telus corporation declared a quarterly dividend on thursday may th shareholders of record on friday june th will be given a dividend of  per share on tuesday july th this represents a  annualized dividend and a yield of  the exdividend date of this dividend is wednesday june th this is a boost from telus corporations previous quarterly dividend of  view telus corporations dividend history how were telus corporations earnings last quarter telus corporation nysetu announced its earnings results on friday august th the company reported  earnings per share for the quarter topping the thomson reuters consensus estimate of  by  the business had re